song.title: Plagarism
song.info:
Plagarism By Fearofdark Finished: 29th August 2009
A song to express my fustraition at this present time. Oddly, inspired by the Po kemon Platinum battle scene against one of the legendary pokemon (no mocking, it's a g ood game!) Made in only a couple of days;...whoa! I'm speedy:D
Samples from aceman and K.Koch, and others from various artists.
You know who you are...oh, and enjoy!
(also, my first chiptune that doesn't really use any guitar or synth samples:) T he strings in this one are unused, and sorry that the ending's a bit sudden, i'm never good at endings:P)
